    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The reason to increase the inclusion slot is so that the formal proofs in those notes (and attached files) is actually correct. One of the scenarios is that there is a reorg and the canonical chain cannot be continued because of the necessary attestations in the attacking withheld branch, that are enough to justify a previous epoch, are not possible to include in the canonical branch anymore. This fix makes it always possible for the honest validators to include possibly withheld attestations",
